-- models/intermediate/int_deduped_billing.sql
```sql
-- Deduplicate billing_events to one row per subscription + event_month (latest event wins)
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        event_id,
        subscription_id,
        event_month,
        amount,
        event_type,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
            PARTITION BY subscription_id, event_month
            ORDER BY event_id DESC
        ) AS row_num
    FROM {{ ref('stg_billing_events') }}
)
SELECT
    event_id,
    subscription_id,
    event_month,
    amount,
    event_type
FROM source
WHERE row_num = 1
```

-- models/mart/fct_monthly_subscription_metrics.sql
```sql
-- Monthly subscription metrics: active subscriptions, MRR, and unique users by month, tier, and industry
WITH billing AS (
    SELECT
        subscription_id,
        event_month,
        amount
    FROM {{ ref('int_deduped_billing') }}
)
SELECT
    b.event_month AS month,
    COALESCE(p.tier, '(unknown)') AS tier,
    COALESCE(co.industry, '(unknown)') AS industry,
    COUNT(DISTINCT s.subscription_id) AS active_subscriptions,
    SUM(b.amount) AS total_mrr,
    COUNT(DISTINCT s.user_id) AS unique_users
FROM billing b
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_subscriptions') }} s
    ON s.subscription_id = b.subscription_id
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_plans') }} p
    ON p.plan_id = s.plan_id
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_users') }} u
    ON u.user_id = s.user_id
LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_companies') }} co
    ON co.company_id = u.company_id
GROUP BY
    b.event_month,
    COALESCE(p.tier, '(unknown)'),
    COALESCE(co.industry, '(unknown)')
ORDER BY
    month ASC,
    tier ASC,
    industry ASC
